    <p>We may collect certain information when you use our app. This includes:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Device Information:</strong> Information about your device, such as the model, OS, and unique identifiers.</li>
        <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Information about your use of the app, including features accessed and interactions.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Permissions We Request</h2>
    <p>Our app requires certain permissions to function properly, including:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>INTERNET:</strong> Allows the app to connect to the internet for data access.</li>
        <li><strong>ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE:</strong> Checks network status for connectivity.</li>
        <li><strong>ACCESS_WIFI_STATE:</strong> Checks Wi-Fi connectivity for optimized usage.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Data Usage</h2>
    <p>We use collected information to improve app performance and user experience. We do not share information with third parties for marketing.</p>

    <h2>Data Security</h2>
    <p>We take security seriously and implement measures to protect your information from unauthorized access or disclosure.</p>

    <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p>We do not knowingly collect information from children under 13. If discovered, such information will be deleted.</p>

